    ArrowFontSize              9

    DividerBackgroundColor     #D5E8D4
    DividerBorderColor         #82B366
    DividerFontSize            11
    DividerFontStyle           bold
    DividerFontColor           #1A3A1A

    GroupBackgroundColor       #FFF9C4
    GroupBorderColor           #F4A261
    GroupFontSize              10
    GroupFontStyle             bold
